# Dashboard env — all OPTIONAL.
#
# The dashboard ships with compiled-in constants for Galileo testnet.
# You can run it with ZERO env vars set. These overrides exist for
# self-hosting on a different chain (e.g., 0G mainnet) — the demo
# path requires nothing here.
#
# Defaults (compiled into apps/dashboard/src/lib/env.ts):
#   ZG_RPC               = https://evmrpc-testnet.0g.ai
#   ZG_INDEXER_RPC       = https://indexer-storage-testnet-turbo.0g.ai
#   AGENTICID_ADDRESS    = 0xd4a5eA2501810d7C81464aa3CdBa58Bfded09E38 (Epic-7 OUR deploy)
#   TEE_VERIFIER_ADDRESS = 0x058fc372562D195F1c2356e4DcFfD94de98Ec3ad (Epic-7 OUR deploy)
#   CHAIN_ID             = 16602
#
# Epic-7 demo session: tokenId 0 on the AgenticID above (rootHash
# 0x53bee8f7174b132fc4e8a85631a41a923a7952117a6e14fdf56fcb1fef6049e6,
# minted 2026-05-10). Visit /verify/0 to see the verifier render.
#
# Network routing: subdomain split (Epic-7). Testnet at root domain
# (verifiable.0g.ai), mainnet at subdomain (mainnet.verifiable.0g.ai).
# Same /verify/<tokenId> path on both. Per-service Coolify env decides
# which network this instance renders.

# === Mainnet service override block (Coolify "mainnet" service) ===
# Uncomment when running the mainnet Coolify service:
# ZG_RPC=https://evmrpc.0g.ai
# ZG_INDEXER_RPC=https://indexer-storage-turbo.0g.ai
# AGENTICID_ADDRESS=0xC6f7fB1511a7483C6e14258c70529e37ec698937
# TEE_VERIFIER_ADDRESS=0x4fffB58B488bBeD9f072Ad68EeB77F643b8858D2
# CHAIN_ID=16661

# === Cross-network site URLs (TopBar's "view <other>" link) ===
# Defaults assume the subdomain split. Override per Coolify service.
# TESTNET_SITE_URL=https://verifiable.0g.ai
# MAINNET_SITE_URL=https://mainnet.verifiable.0g.ai

# === Legacy alias (still accepted by the code, prefer ZG_RPC above) ===
# Older .env files used ZG_TESTNET_RPC; loadEnv() reads it as a fallback.
# ZG_TESTNET_RPC=https://evmrpc-testnet.0g.ai
